  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we noted the results as mixed and inconclusive as to whether VIADS is helpful in the hypothesis generation process.",
    "The role of VIADS in hypothesis generation may be more complicated than that of linear effects.",
    "A larger-scale study with more functional tools focusing on hypothesis generation would likely generate more generalizable results, considering that VIADS is a secondary data analytical tool that was not developed primarily to facilitate hypothesis generation.",
    "Scientific hypothesis generation, which aims at developing research projects to pursue later, can be categorized into at least two broad groups.",
    "The first category typically originates from observing expected or unexpected phenomena during wetlab experiments or other types of data collection, such as in traditional chemical or biological studies."
